rComments: Believes she is all knowledgeable, not open to interpretation or discussion.

Although i kept telling myself that going to class was probably a waste of time.  I soon realized after taking her course that I learned A LOT!!!  From essay writting to fact learning.  Definatly was worth it in the end.

I don't know what everyone is complaining about.  I found Professor Bonner to be organized and concise. Her class always seemed to go by really quickly.  She made her expectations clear and the marking was more than fair...both my roomate and I thought that the marking was even too easy.

Very disappointed, she nailed our class with 80% of your final grade on the day of the final, because thats when we recieved our essays back, on top of this the grader doesn't make much sense with comments and Bonner isn't very clear on some topics.

Very well-organised course and she knows the course mateiral like the bof her hand She will make you learn. Unfortunately, she will disgust you with academic life: she is a strict, unfair and above all irrational and nonsensical marker. Very narrow-minded, she will not allow you to write a report that might betray her ideology. Avoid at all costs.

She has a chip on her shoulder. Enjoys making students suffer, raise their hopes and then thrashing and burning them with impossible expectations and ridiculously high standards AND refusing to reward A+'s because "there are no perfect answers in political science". She's totally insane. Avoid her.
If you are looking to improve your writing and advance yourself academically, you should take htis course. She is a hard marker, but she really knows her stuff!

Very good prof who knows the subject matter very well. Her lectures are clear, organised, and informative, yet concise. Unfortunately, she is narrow-minded, very strict, and sees a B as being a very successful grade. Be prepared for a drop in your GPA if you have her.

Expects extremely simple essays, anything interesting or beyond a+b=c and you're going to lose marks.  Remember those essays you wrote in grade 9??  That's what she's looking for.  Meanwhile the material is really dry, and she is very condescending.  I would recommend avoiding her classes unless they are required for your program.

Very clear and organized teaching.  you will learn a lot, and she know's what she's talking about.  However, hardest marker I've ever had.  I know many students who dropped her course when they found out she was the prof.  If you're looking for a good mark, be prepared to work work work (and it still might not happen).  She's ridiculous!

Pedantic. Dull. Long winded. Insanely high expectations despite lack of class content. I honestly have never been so bored in my life. I am immensely disappointed with this class and this prof. I honestly will never take another class from her.... RUN KIDS RUN!!!!!

Very simplistic class on Latin America Politics. You might as well take HIS2117. She makes overheads with lists of presidents. You lose marks on the paper if you are too 'descriptive'..and yet..that is all this class has been...

Prof. Bonner is a very hard marker but I must admit that being in her class prepared me to do better work. At least she gives clear explainations of what she expects. If you are not willing to put a lot of work in, then I would skip this prof.
why hasn't Ottawa U fired her yet???? I'm baffled. There have been several formal complaints made about her. Do not take any course she teaches.....you'll regret it if you do

A very hard marker. Did not seem to notice improvements in effort or work, therefore regardless of effort you will likely receive the same mark for all of your assignments based on the 1st assignment. Seemed very nervous while lecturing the class.
hope i'd dropped it =(

WORST PROF EVER!!! Got flustered/confused/lost several times... Cannot stray from her notes or else her lack of knowledge will show!! Skip this course...why bother torturing yourself!?!?!

Do you think that you can write six essays in two hours for a final exam? If you can, then you should take this class. Reading her comments on my term paper was worse then getting dragged naked over glass. She is a very hard marker.
Be prepared for a drop in your grade point average if you take a class with her.
This prof is on a major power-trip and doesn't seem to enjoy teaching at all. Worst prof ever.
Oh dear, where to start.  Doesn't speak any language properly, doesn't clarify, is egotistical, unhelpful, and OH. SO. BORING.
She is the worst professor I have ever had. Hands down.

is an okay prof; needs to learn how to use the technology and not overheads; interesting class with good readings!
